# 🤖 Earnings Call Sentiment Dashboard (GPT-4 powered)

A simple, investor-grade Streamlit app that uses OpenAI GPT-4-turbo to analyze earnings call transcripts and extract:

- 📊 Sentiment breakdown (% Positive / Neutral / Negative)
- 🧠 Overall tone (Optimistic, Neutral, Cautiously Optimistic, etc.)
- 🗣️ Key management quotes with tone labels
- ✅ Business takeaways (revenue, margins, guidance, risks)
- 📈 Industry trends and 🧪 product mix insights
- 🏢 Auto-detects Company Name + Sector

